==已取消==
===《惩罚者2》===
2004年版《惩罚者》的票房表现感到失望，但是狮门娱乐对续集的DVD销售感兴趣。Jonathan Hensleigh和托马斯·简也着手续集的拍摄，尽管有许多作家写剧本仍然缺乏好的剧本，并花了3年时间。托马斯·简希望能拍续集，并说：“这将是黑暗的，血腥，比上部更不友好的电影。”然而，Kurt Sutter看了新剧本后，他说：“我不会为一部我不相信的电影花费我生命中的几个月时间，我喜欢漫威的伙计，并祝福他们。同时，我将继续寻找一部电影，希望粉丝们都叫我看的电影。<ref>{{cite news | url=http://www.superherohype.com/news/topnews.php?id=5685 | title=Thomas Jane Pull out of Punisher 2 | publisher=SuperHeroHype.com | date=2007-05-15 | accessdate=2015-09-07 | archive-date=2009-08-02 | archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20090802193303/http://www.superherohype.com/news/topnews.php?id=5685 | dead-url=yes }}</ref><ref>{{cite news| url=http://www.aintitcool.com/node/32673| title=AICN Exclusive: Thomas Jane dropping out of PUNISHER 2?!?| publisher=aintitcool.com| date=May 15, 2007 <!--- 6:25pm-->| accessdate=2015-09-07| archive-date=2012-08-06| archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20120806015728/http://www.aintitcool.com/node/32673| dead-url=no}}</ref>
==未来==
雷·史蒂文森表示对惩罚者续集感兴趣，对Barracuda暗示他可能会扮演反派。<ref name=ignvideos>[http://media.movies.ign.com/media/382/382367/vids_1.html IGN Punisher: War Zone Trailer, Videos and Movies] {{webarchive|url=https://web.archive.org/web/20080914141031/http://media.movies.ign.com/media/382/382367/vids_1.html |date=2008-09-14 }}</ref> 在2008年圣地亚哥动漫展，当记者问他是否签署了更多的惩罚者电影时，他说“如果我愿意，当然会签署。这要有粉丝基础。如果这行得通，我们会再次开始。”<ref name=ignvideos/>

在2010年圣地亚哥动漫展，漫威工作室证实，他们已收回惩罚者的电影版权，他们希望惩罚者能很快出现在屏幕上。<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.cinematical.com/2010/07/26/sdcc-marvel-regains-film-rights-for-the-punisher/|title=SDCC: Marvel Regains Film Rights for 'The Punisher'|accessdate=2015-09-07|archive-date=2019-08-22|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190822162657/http://www.cinematical.com/2010/07/26/sdcc-marvel-regains-film-rights-for-the-punisher/|dead-url=no}}</ref>在接受Bleeding Cool采访时，菲戈曾谈到希望惩罚者能出现在重启版《夜魔侠》中。<ref>{{Cite web |url=http://www.bleedingcool.com/2013/10/20/marvels-kevin-feige-were-trying-to-figure-out-what-to-do-with-daredevil-now/ |title=Marvel’s Kevin Feige – “We’re Trying To Figure Out What To Do With Daredevil Now” |accessdate=2015-09-07 |archive-date=2015-09-08 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150908055637/http://www.bleedingcool.com/2013/10/20/marvels-kevin-feige-were-trying-to-figure-out-what-to-do-with-daredevil-now/ |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref>{{cite web|title=Daredevil could spin off into “hard R” Punisher reboot|url=http://www.scifinow.co.uk/news/daredevil-could-spin-off-into-hard-r-punisher-show/|publisher=SciFiNow|date=2015-03-31|accessdate=2015-06-01|archive-date=2017-08-20|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170820035149/https://www.scifinow.co.uk/news/daredevil-could-spin-off-into-hard-r-punisher-show/|dead-url=no}}</ref>

在2015年1月，托马斯·简称他并不想再次扮演惩罚者，除非有好的剧本。<ref>{{cite web|title=Will Thomas Jane Return as ‘The Punisher’ on Netflix?|url=http://movieweb.com/punisher-movie-tv-thomas-jane-netflix-series/|publisher=Movieweb|date=2015-01-23|accessdate=2015-06-01|archive-date=2015-05-26|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150526012432/http://movieweb.com/punisher-movie-tv-thomas-jane-netflix-series/|dead-url=no}}</ref>

